NETMOX is the software which stands for Network Monitoring and Controlling.
NETMOX is a networking tool designed to monitor and control LAN-based networks.

It lets you monitor the activity of all the PCs remotely. Also you can share your screen with clients and control other system processes. It can be used for monitoring your clients’ activities on remote terminals. Simultaneous execution of various commands is possible. It makes live demonstration which makes presentation much easier in LAN networks. It allows full control of clients in offices, labs and other LAN networks. It makes message communication and interaction possible between two or more computers.